OL,7,FAn inquest into their deaths, which
OL,8,Fwas held at Crook Coroner's Court on
OL,9,FFriday 25 October, heard Mr Hodgson,
OL,10,Fhad been severely intoxicated on drugs
OL,11,Fand was disqualified from driving at
OL,12,Fthe time of the crash.
OL,14,FIt happened on Middridge Road, near
OL,15,Fthe Rushyford roundabout, shortly
OL,16,Fbefore noon on Friday 5 July.
