OL,3,CMoped rider was 'significantly
OL,4,Cintoxicated' before crash which killed
OL,5,Cteens
OL,7,FThe inquest heard both teenagers had
OL,8,Fbeen seen on CCTV and by witnesses
OL,9,Flooking over their shoulders in the
OL,10,Fminutes before the crash, as though
OL,11,Fthey were watching out for something.
OL,13,FTheir moped, which did not have an
OL,14,FMOT, struck a car which was stationary
OL,15,Fon the road, causing it to wobble and
OL,16,Ffall onto the other carriageway. It
OL,17,Fwas then hit by a car travelling in
OL,18,Fthe opposite direction.
OL,20,FMr Hodgson died at the scene, while
OL,21,FBobby later died in hospital.
