OL,7,FMore than a dozen members of their
OL,8,Ffamilies attended the hearing on
OL,9,FFriday.
OL,11,FFollowing the crash, Mr Hodgson's
OL,12,Ffamily said in a statement: "Wayne,
OL,13,Fyou have left a massive hole in our
OL,14,Fhearts and lives. You are going to be
OL,15,Fmissed for forever and a day. We love
OL,16,Fyou always, our baby Wayne."
OL,18,FBobby's family said: "Bobby was a
OL,19,Fgreatly-loved son, brother, nephew,
OL,20,Fcousin, grandson.
