OL,7,F"He was a cheeky boy who loved to say
OL,8,F'wise man'. He will never be forgotten
OL,9,Fand missed forever".
OL,11,FCoroner Jeremy Chipperfield returned a
OL,12,Fverdict of death by misadventure for
OL,13,FWayne Hodgson and one of accidental
OL,14,Fdeath for Bobby.
OL,16,FHe told their families today he could
OL,17,Fnot imagine how hard it was to listen
OL,18,Fto the evidence and thanked them for
OL,19,Fthe composure they had shown.
